Package nano.remexp.client.layouts

Class Summary
GLAdmin The administrator GUI module with all possible controls.
GLAdvanced The advanced GUI layout that has no input line like the administrator, but has the movement arrows that allow some movements to certain deltas on the sample.
GLController The GUI layout that has the basic controls.
GLObserver The observer GUI layout that only has passive modules to display state information.
GUILayout The super class for the GUI layouts.
